'''珍珠廣場'''（{{lang-ar|دوار اللؤلؤ}}），巴林政府稱為「'''海灣合作委員會廣場'''」<ref name=MSNBC>{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/42125406/ns/world_news-mideastn_africa/|title=Bahrain demolishes square used by protesters|publisher=MSNBC|accessdate=2011-03-19|archive-date=2011-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110319045947/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/42125406/ns/world_news-mideastn_africa/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[巴林|巴林]]首都[[麥納麥|麥納麥]]金融區附近的[[迴旋處|迴旋處]]。珍珠廣場是進入首都多條路線的主要交匯處，鄰近多個地標，如[[巴林世界貿易中心|巴林世界貿易中心]]。

2011年，巴林爆發[[2011年巴林反政府示威|反政府示威]]，示威者聚集於珍珠廣場。3月16日，政府驅散示威者陣營，兩日後，廣場中央的'''珍珠紀念塔'''被政府夷平。

== 珍珠紀念塔 ==
1982年[[海灣合作委員會|海灣合作委員會]]第6次會議期間，珍珠紀念塔豎立在迴旋處中央<ref name=yalibnan/><ref name=haaretz/>。紀念塔由6張獨桅帆船的帆組成，承托着上方的[[珍珠|珍珠]]。6張帆象徵海灣六國，珍珠象徵共同的傳統和巴林的養珠業歷史<ref>{{en}}[http://www.bahrainembassy.org/index.cfm?fuseaction=document.home&id=75 Bahrain: Two Million Tourists Can't Be Wrong] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bahrainembassy.org/index.cfm?fuseaction=document.home&id=75 |date=20110609113203 }} April 17, 2007, Bahrain Embassy</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/bahrain/8390773/Bahrain-authorities-destroy-Pearl-Roundabout.html |title=Bahrain authorities destroy Pearl Roundabout |publisher=The Telegraph |accessdate=2011-03-19 |archive-date=2011-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110322053958/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/bahrain/8390773/Bahrain-authorities-destroy-Pearl-Roundabout.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。紀念塔的圖樣出現在500[[巴林第納爾|費爾]]硬幣上，500費爾是巴林最大面值的流通硬幣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.cbb.gov.bh/page.php?p=current_coins_500fils |title=Current Coins: 500 fils |publisher=Central Bank of Bahrain |accessdate=2011-03-19 |archive-date=2012-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315183708/http://www.cbb.gov.bh/page.php?p=current_coins_500fils |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年3月18日上午，政府拆毀珍珠紀念塔。政府在電視上解釋，反政府示威者「冒犯」和「褻瀆」了紀念塔，因此必須把它「潔淨」<ref name=MSNBC/><ref name=haaretz>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/bahrain-tears-down-statue-at-focus-of-anti-monarchy-protests-1.350056 |title=Bahrain tears down statue at focus of anti-monarchy protests |publisher=Haaretz |accessdate=2011-03-19 |archive-date=2011-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110321122823/http://www.haaretz.com/news/international/bahrain-tears-down-statue-at-focus-of-anti-monarchy-protests-1.350056 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 2011年反政府示威 ==
{{main|2011年巴林反政府示威}}
2011年2月起，巴林的反政府示威者在珍珠廣場示威<ref name=nytimes>{{en}}{{cite news|first=|last=|title=Unrest Grows in Bahrain as Police Kill a 2nd Protester|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/02/16/world/middleeast/16bahrain.html?partner=rss&emc=rss|work=New York Times|publisher=|date=2011-02-15|accessdate=2011-02-15|archive-date=2012-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115074318/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/02/16/world/middleeast/16bahrain.html?partner=rss&emc=rss|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=yalibnan>{{cite news|first=|last=|title=Second Man Dies in Bahrain Skirmishes|url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2011/02/15/second-man-dies-in-bahrain-skirmishes/|work=Ya Libnan|publisher=|date=2011-02-15|accessdate=2011-02-15|archive-date=2011-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110217030230/http://www.yalibnan.com/2011/02/15/second-man-dies-in-bahrain-skirmishes/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=channel4>{{en}}{{cite news |first= |last= |title=Thousands gather at Bahrain's 'Tahrir Square' |url=http://www.channel4.com/news/thousands-gather-at-bahrains-tahrir-square |work=Channel 4 News |publisher= |date=2011-02-15 |accessdate=2011-02-15 |archive-date=2011-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110219030447/http://www.channel4.com/news/thousands-gather-at-bahrains-tahrir-square |dead-url=no }}</ref>，示威者將珍珠廣場比作埃及開羅的[[解放廣場|解放廣場]]，即[[2011年埃及革命|2011年埃及革命]]的主要示威地點<ref name=channel4/>。

2月17日，示威者在廣場過夜時，警隊在3時嘗試清場，造成多人受傷，最少6名平民死亡<ref>{{en}}[http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/02/201121714223324820.html] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5wZPVZfFG?url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/02/201121714223324820.html |date=20110217175913 |dateformat=iso }}</ref>。事後，警官哈森表示，早前已警告過示威者，但他們拒絕離開，而且示威者持有刀械和手槍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.akhbaralarab.net/index.php/regional/33378-2011-02-17-15-17-04 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723005759/http://www.akhbaralarab.net/index.php/regional/33378-2011-02-17-15-17-04 |archivedate=2011-07-23 }}</ref>。[[巴林國防軍|巴林國防軍]]坦克佔領廣場，阻止示威者再度在該處聚集<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.liveleak.com/view?i=59d_1297947065 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-03-19 |archive-date=2011-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318211111/http://www.liveleak.com/view?i=59d_1297947065 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。醫院附近的示威者嘗試再度佔領廣場，但被在廣場駐守的軍隊射擊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/02/20112184122210251.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-03-19 |archive-date=2011-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110806083412/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/02/20112184122210251.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

其後，巴林王儲[[薩勒曼·本·哈邁德·本·伊薩·阿勒哈利法|薩勒曼·阿勒哈利法]]在電視上要求各方保持克制<ref>〔http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2011/0220/breaking12.html〕 {{Wayback|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2011/0220/breaking12.html |date=20110227000022 }}</ref>。翌日，他下令軍隊坦克離開廣場，並容許示威者和平佔據該處，更保證他們能繼續示威而不會再受攻擊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://articles.cnn.com/2011-02-19/world/bahrain.protests_1_protesters-bahrainis-security-forces?_s=PM:WORLD |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-03-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110322020057/http://articles.cnn.com/2011-02-19/world/bahrain.protests_1_protesters-bahrainis-security-forces?_s=PM:WORLD |archivedate=2011-03-22 }}</ref>。然而，在3月16日，巴林國防軍、防暴警察和[[半島防衞軍|半島防衞軍]]推倒並焚燒示威者帳蓬<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/42124501/ |title='Business-Friendly Bahrain' Disappears; Ex-Pats Exit |publisher=CNBC |accessdate=2011-03-19 |archive-date=2011-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110612053537/http://www.cnbc.com/id/42124501/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=MSNBC/>。

